msgid ""
"[Flakes aren't real and cannot hurt you: a guide to using Nix flakes the non-"
"flake way](https://jade.fyi/blog/flakes-arent-real/) (Jade Lovelace, January "
"2024)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../concepts/flakes.md:114
msgid ""
"[Nix Flakes is an experiment that did too much at once...](https://samuel."
"dionne-riel.com/blog/2023/09/06/flakes-is-an-experiment-that-did-too-much-at-"
