"experiment-that-did-too-much-at-once/32707)) (Samuel Dionne-Riel, September "
"2023)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../concepts/flakes.md:115
msgid ""
"[Experimental does not mean unstable](https://determinate.systems/posts/"
"experimental-does-not-mean-unstable) ([comments](https://discourse.nixos.org/"
"t/experimental-does-not-mean-unstable-detsyss-perspective-on-nix-"
"flakes/32703)) (Graham Christensen, September 2023)"
msgstr ""

